(secondQuint)A Study to Evaluate the Safety and Efficacy of Relugolix in Men With Advanced Prostate Cancer.

 This study is an international phase 3 randomized, open-label, parallel group efficacy and safety study to evaluate oral daily relugolix 120 mg in patients with androgen-sensitive advanced prostate cancer who require at least 1 year (48 weeks) of continuous androgen deprivation therapy.

